metadata.name: "What is Humanity?"
metadata.description:
I wouldn't lie on the floor and cry
If everything was better
Time running faster
But we are still alone

When darkness dispelled our fear
We ended up with ourselves
What's in it?
I am flesh and here
Fury and anger
Am i human?
What is humanity?

Nox sang songs about light
With understanding
Taking on the guise of hope
But we're standing here
Look at me I am the Lumos

Take away my fears
give me sleep
Give me the dawn
give me a hope
Always finding time for love
_

Her name is 𝕷𝖚𝖒𝖔𝖘 𝖙𝖍𝖊 𝖈𝖆𝖙.
She is Cat in Human body.
Maybe you know her sister? (𝕹𝖔𝖝 𝖙𝖍𝖊 𝕮𝖆𝖙)
_
Technical info:

Render: Nvidia IRAY
Motion Capture: IPad pro (m1 ver)
Edit: AE, Premiere
Vocal: Vocaloid
Instrumental: FL Studio
